    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ROVA is a cozy space-rover photography game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help a new space colony conduct research on large spherical planets, by documenting  <br>elements of alien worlds through photography. ROVA is a game about discovery and  <br>exploration.  <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/23da0150c33c1d93827318d58edc5e91.poster.avif?t=1771963288\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/23da0150c33c1d93827318d58edc5e91.webm?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/23da0150c33c1d93827318d58edc5e91.mp4?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SPACE-ROVA PHOTOGRAPHY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photograph EVERYTHING, with your very own ROVA.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/23d02cf3ba699cfb04fb065997812081.poster.avif?t=1771963288\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/23d02cf3ba699cfb04fb065997812081.webm?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/23d02cf3ba699cfb04fb065997812081.mp4?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FULLY EXPLORABLE PLANETS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore entire alien planets packed with research opportunities, just waiting to be discovered  <br>through your photography.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/a09243ed03c720224eff8c5b1ee0b5b0.poster.avif?t=1771963288\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/a09243ed03c720224eff8c5b1ee0b5b0.webm?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/a09243ed03c720224eff8c5b1ee0b5b0.mp4?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RESEARCH DATABASE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each photo you take expands the Research Database. Can you find everything there is  <br>to discover?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/1855f1302aa8bcdd7714a8448f58a090.poster.avif?t=1771963288\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/1855f1302aa8bcdd7714a8448f58a090.webm?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/1855f1302aa8bcdd7714a8448f58a090.mp4?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>COLONIST CUSTOMISATION</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space research in style. Customise the colony with a range of clothing options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/b75eee0c2bfba5e69be3308242ae7e44.poster.avif?t=1771963288\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/b75eee0c2bfba5e69be3308242ae7e44.webm?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147020/extras/b75eee0c2bfba5e69be3308242ae7e44.mp4?t=1771963288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Space-ROVA photography </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Research Database: grows with every photo you take!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple planets with their own unique biomes and ecosystems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save your photos to your PC. Perfect for desktop backgrounds or  <br>sharing with friends!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Colonist customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 'Observation/study mode' - listen to lofi songs whilst observing colonists perform  <br>their daily routines  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
